}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The serial number of the hub populating this entry is '''CZ'''''83393480''.
The '''[[Belkin]]''' logo, "F5U304", and "REV:2.0/1.6mm" is silkscreened on the board. :The hub's board is using all '''Canicon''' electrolytic capacitors.
The power adapter included with the hub appears to have been an ''unbranded'' PS0526 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.5-2.6A).
